{
  "id": "019cdcdc-fd01-7d11-b0d7-a773d2aadb3d",
  "content": "### New Subcommand Group\n### Existing Command Adaptation\n\n### What `corvia workspace create` Does\n\n1. Creates `<name>/` directory\n2. Generates `corvia.toml` with `[workspace]` section from `--repo` flags\n3. If `--template` provided, clones template and adapts config\n4. Runs `corvia workspace init` (clones repos, initializes `.corvia/`)\n5. Runs first ingest of all repos\n",
